<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idee684400-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9" identifier="/us/usc/t7/s954"><num value="954">§ 954.</num><heading> Grades and standards for classification</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary is authorized to establish and promulgate grades and standards for the classification of peanuts, whenever in his discretion he may see fit.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idee684401-3a6e-11f1-addd-bbaf0b3f68e9">(<ref href="/us/act/1936-06-24/ch745/s4">June 24, 1936, ch. 745, § 4</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/49/1899">49 Stat. 1899</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
